01:37:41.664 --> 01:37:44.709
<i>This is officer Finnegan
from the State Penitentiary Walla Walla.</i>

01:37:44.876 --> 01:37:47.879
<i>I'm placing a call from John Forster
to his attorney Lydia Doherty.</i>

01:37:47.962 --> 01:37:49.255
Put him through.

01:37:50.215 --> 01:37:51.549
<i>Go ahead.</i>

01:37:51.633 --> 01:37:52.759
Lydia.

01:37:54.010 --> 01:37:55.428
Did you finish with Gramm?

01:37:55.637 --> 01:37:58.014
